## Handling Common UI Elements

### Cookie Consent Banner
```typescript
// Dismiss cookie consent if present
const acceptBtn = page.locator('app-cookie-consent button')
  .filter({ hasText: /Accept|Zaakceptuj/i }).first();
if (await acceptBtn.isVisible({ timeout: 2000 }).catch(() => false)) {
  await acceptBtn.click();
  await page.waitForTimeout(500);
}
```

### PrimeNG Components
```typescript
// p-menu popup
const userProfile = page.locator('[data-testid="user-profile-button"]');
await userProfile.click({ force: true }); // Force click bypasses overlays

// Wait for popup menu
const menu = page.locator('body > p-menu .p-menu');
await menu.waitFor({ state: 'visible' });

// Click menu item
const menuItem = page.locator('.p-menuitem-link')
  .filter({ has: page.locator('.pi-sign-out') });
await menuItem.click();
```

### Loading States
```typescript
// Wait for loading spinner to disappear
await page.locator('[data-testid="loading-spinner"]')
  .waitFor({ state: 'hidden', timeout: 30000 });

// Or use page object method
await myPage.waitForLoadingComplete();
```

