## Running Tests

### Local Development
```bash
# Run all smoke tests
npx playwright test --grep "@smoke"

# Run specific feature tests
npx playwright test tests/specs/properties/

# Run in headed mode for debugging
npx playwright test --headed --grep "@smoke"

# Run with UI mode
npx playwright test --ui

# Generate HTML report
npx playwright test --reporter=html
npx playwright show-report
```

### Environment Configuration
```bash
# Discover Aspire ports
bash tests/config/discover-ports.sh > tests/.env

# Run against staging
TEST_ENV=staging npx playwright test --grep "@prod"

# Skip health checks
REQUIRE_SERVICES_HEALTHY=false npx playwright test
```

